=== Advantage 1 – Self-Determination ===&#xD;
&#xD;
(% class=&amp;#34;western&amp;#34; %)&#xD;
==== Financial incentives disproportionately reward non-tribal businesses ====&#xD;
&#xD;
(% style=&amp;#34;margin-bottom: 0in&amp;#34; %)&#xD;
(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:1.0em;&amp;#34; %)**UConn Law Review, April 2012**&#xD;
