James (% style=&amp;#34;font-size: 1em; background: rgb(0, 255, 255)&amp;#34; %)**Hansen**(%%), (% style=&amp;#34;font-size: 1em; background: rgb(0, 255, 255)&amp;#34; %)**NASA space studies director**(%%), 5/9/(% style=&amp;#34;font-size: 1em; background: rgb(0, 255, 255)&amp;#34; %)**12**(%%), Game Over for the Climate, http:~/~/www.nytimes.com/2012/05/10/opinion/game-over-for-the-climate.html?_r=2andpartner=rssnytandemc=rss [DCL PRE] [Language edited – Indigenized]&#xD;
