(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:1.0em;&amp;#34; %)**Plan: The United States Federal Government should offer a cash grant equal to 30% of the cost of wind or solar facilities for projects owned by a corporation or government of Indigenous Peoples in the United States or any partnership of which a corporation or government of Indigenous Peoples in the United States is a partner or holder of equity interest that would otherwise qualify for an Investment Tax Credit or a Production Tax Credit for a wind or solar project.**&#xD;
